            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>New UI themes, full Spanish support, and server optimisation fixes.</p>
<!-- -->
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="new-ui">New UI<a href="https://iliiasik.github.io/MThoughts-Wiki/blog/2026/06/11/version-1-4-1#new-ui" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to New UI" title="Direct link to New UI" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<p>Reworked <strong>Vanilla</strong> and <strong>Classic</strong> themes, and added two brand new ones — <strong>Magic</strong> and <strong>Tech</strong>.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="added-spanish">Added Spanish<a href="https://iliiasik.github.io/MThoughts-Wiki/blog/2026/06/11/version-1-4-1#added-spanish" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Added Spanish" title="Direct link to Added Spanish" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<p>Full Spanish support including custom facts, nightmares, and all overlay text.</p>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="server-optimisation-fixes">Server optimisation fixes<a href="https://iliiasik.github.io/MThoughts-Wiki/blog/2026/06/11/version-1-4-1#server-optimisation-fixes" class="hash-link" aria-label="Direct link to Server optimisation fixes" title="Direct link to Server optimisation fixes" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<p>Various server-side performance improvements.</p>]]></content:encoded>
